com.thomsonreuters.upa.valueadd.domainrep.rdm.login

Interface LoginMsg

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MsgBase
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    LoginAck, LoginClose, LoginConsumerConnectionStatus, LoginPost, LoginRefresh, LoginRequest, LoginStatus

    public interface LoginMsg
extends MsgBase
    The RDM Login Base Message. This RDM dictionary messages may be reused or pooled in a single collection via their common LoginMsg interface and re-used as a different LoginMsgType. RDMDictionaryMsgType member may be set to one of these to indicate the specific RDMDictionaryMsg class.
    See Also:
    LoginClose, LoginRefresh, LoginRequest, LoginStatus, LoginAck, LoginPost, LoginConsumerConnectionStatus, - Factory for creating RDM login messages, LoginMsgType
